      "raw_text": "The Press expose Of the\nattempt made by the Great\nNorthern to bind It's en-\npIoyes at HilIyard to vote\nfor the company's choice Of\ncandidates lie the political\nsensation Of the day.\n\n\nThe Press is willing to\ngrant the company space for\nany statement Il cares to\nmake on the question, but\ninvestigation already made\nprompts the assumption that\nno explanation of the COM\npany's attitude can be made\nthat will square with the\nprinciple Of free suffrage."
